<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="5" />!<delay20 /> <anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Bwa ha ha ha!</message>
	<message label="204" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Clapping" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Ich werde versuchen, Sätze zu
bilden, die nur aus <tag a="110" b="5" />
